name: Super Smash Sisters (hi sisters!)
description:
It's here, and ruder than anything else on the planet!

This highly critically acclaimed fighting games features all the best characters from Devil May Cry:

Mr. Eugene H Krabs, Austin 'PBG' PeanutButterGamer, The Eiffel Tower, Potassium, Waluigi, Wario, Taylor Swift and Bob Belcher all appear in this brilliant game!

And now with 4 expanisve stages! Thatcher Land, Spain, Dream and Tubbo and ofcourse, the tournament favourite - Dr Phil's The Ranch

COMING SOON!

Assist Trophies - Donald J. Trump, CDI Link, Lonk, jSchlatt, Digimon Poop, Nigel Farrage, Memeulous, ThatVeganTeacher, White Van, Bender, Herbert The Pervert, GTA V Taxi, Meg Griffin and Facebook.

Stages - Malaysia Airlines Flight 370,  World Trade Centre and Twin Towers (11th of September 2001 Edition), Bin Weevils Server and Jimmy Saville World,
